 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc8c7d63b81543c540ef2aa3d3c5ac1f9016299","tid":166350,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又食牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日邊似牛肺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nM男是咪屌得牛肺多搞到睇咩都覺得似牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你哪有囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n【願90歲復出】80歲生日拍告別作 日本最老AV女優引退</blockquote><br />\n80歲，又乾又摷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ed7c755b391f3695d0be4773d75393cf3e268b","tid":166350,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又食牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日邊似牛肺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nM男是咪屌得牛肺多搞到睇咩都覺得似牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你哪有囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你好賤格啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住呀m男我知錯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日蝦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fd76674fc0360b7d182a89839282f89c4f4fe6","tid":166350,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又食牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日邊似牛肺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nM男是咪屌得牛肺多搞到睇咩都覺得似牛肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你哪有囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n【願90歲復出】80歲生日拍告別作 日本最老AV女優引退</blockquote><br />\n80歲，又乾又摷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n【願90歲復出】80歲生日拍告別作 日本最老AV女優引退<br />\n<br />\n日本最年長色情影片女星、80歲的帝塚真織宣佈引退。不過各位支持者無須太傷心，皆因帝塚與很多色情影片女星一樣，引退後不排除會復出。<br />\n<br />\n帝塚真織生於1936年，是位歌劇團歌手，9年前以71歲之齡當上色情影片女星，拍過數十部作品。至於引退的理由，她歸咎是業界欠缺血氣方剛的精壯猛男做對手。帝塚如是道：「燈光一亮起，你就會做到最好。我無遺憾，但當對手不是我杯茶時，拍攝就變得困難。」<br />\n<br />\n帝塚在80歲生日拍攝告別作，但她已聲言只要有人向她招手，就算90歲都會再次復出。帝塚說：「我從來不是看錢的。早已有人問我在兩或三年內復出（的可能性），我說我會考慮。」<br />\n<br />\n銀髮族色情其實不是僅僅迎合「重口味」，而是色情業龐大的巿場，因為全國超過四分一人，即3400萬人超過65歲。日本色情業每年投資約200億美元（1560億港元），業內人士指，有多達四分一正是包含這類老人元素。<br />\n<br />\n法新社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170322&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56459713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170322%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56459713&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4572efe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170322%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56459713&h=1134e53a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170322&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56459713</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ozxln6cj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fozxln6cj&h=993d6892&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c56c39adbeafec9c0920b065ac69ea192f27795","tid":166350,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又食牛肺<img src=\